  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@timkelty Sorry this is a documentation mistake, the helper you are being given in searchFunction only has the  \"helper.search()\" method on it.\r\n\r\nHere's how to use it:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n  searchFunction: function(helper) {\r\n    search.helper.anyHelperMethod();\r\n    search.helper.anyHelperMethod();\r\n    helper.search(); // trigger a new search\r\n  }\r\n})\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2017-01-13T11:58:00Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/873#issuecomment-272427266",
    "id": 272427266,
